<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4326761>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ventral views of head from various Pyrgomorphidae genera. (A) Chrotogonus; (B) Tenuitarsus; (C) Aularches; (D) Chlorizeina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4326761/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4326763>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dorsal views of pronotum from various Pyrgomorphidae genera. (A) Chrotogonus; (B) Orthacris; (C) Nilgiracris; (D) Poekilocerus; (E) Mekongiella" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4326763/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4326765>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Comparison of hind legs between (A) Chrotogonus and (B) Tenuitarsus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4326765/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4326769>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Comparison of epiphallus between (A) Chrotogonus and (B) Tenuitarsus. Scale bar = 0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4326769/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4326799>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Lateral and dorsal views of Pyrgomorphidae species occurring in Indian subcontinent. (A, C) Tenuitarsus angustus; (B, D) Mekongiella kingdoni; (E, G) Chrotogonus trachypterus; (F, H) Rakwana ornata. Scale bar = 5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4326799/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4326771>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Wing length variation in Pyrgomorphidae. Apterous: (A) Nilgiracris, (B) Orthacris, (C) Mekongiella; Micropterous: (D) Colemania; Brachypterous: (E) Zarytes; Macropterous: (F) Atractomorpha." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4326771/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4326773>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Hind tarsus. (A) Rakwana; (B) Mekongiella." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4326773/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

